      <title>韩国监管机构加大力度打击与中国相关的票据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/south-korea-watchdog-intensifies-crackdown-on-china-linked-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国监管机构正在对出售与中国股票相关的奇异票据的当地银行和经纪商展开更广泛的调查，担心这些证券可能会让投资者蒙受重大损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/south-korea-watchdog-intensifies-crackdown-on-china-linked-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 01:50:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特降价应对中东供应风险，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯下调所有地区的官方售价后，油价下跌，凸显了前景恶化，并盖过了对红海紧张局势和利比亚供应中断的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国科技股暴跌，亚洲股市下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/asia-shares-to-open-flat-as-inflation-data-looms-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心博彩业监管收紧以及政府提振经济的力度不够，亚洲股市下跌，香港科技股遭抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/asia-shares-to-open-flat-as-inflation-data-looms-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 22:29:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
